item.description:
What makes a woke theory &ldquo;Critical?&rdquo;
Understanding what the woke mean when they use the term &ldquo;critical,&rdquo; and how that differs from the enlightenment liberal notion of &ldquo;critical thinking.&rdquo;
If there was a single word that summed up the thinking at the heart of Critical Social Justice (AKA wokeness) it is the word ‘critical.’ In the academic world Critical Social Justice Theorists have come up with a great number of theories which they call critical: Critical Pedagogy, Critical Race Theory, Critical Queer Theory, Critical Race Pedagogy, Critical Dietetics, Critical Legal Studies, and so on.
